### 3. MONITORING: VIEW ALL COLLECTED DATA
GET http://localhost:8080/api/search-bid/all
Accept: application/json

### 4. EXECUTE AI MATCHING (Trigger Python)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matching/run
Accept: application/json

### 5. MONITORING: VIEW REGISTERED USERS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Accept: application/json

